comments: You\'ll need the book ($$$) to get access to the hw, not hard but there is a TON of it for each chapter. Tests are mostly written, and some fill in the blank/MC. You will have discussions due on canvas as well. It\'s best to know some Spanish before you take this class, NOT BEGINNER FRIENDLY. I found her to be cold and not will not work with you.

comments: I have spent the better part of the past 14 weeks in this class. The professor is nice and friendly. But I have not understood what we were doing almost from day one. This class is more geared to those who already speak Spanish and need the credit. If you don\'t already speak Spanish, go elsewhere. This class won\'t help you.

comments: Professor Winkler was outstnading! She was always willing and available to help with any questions I may have had. I would definitely take her class again. I had her for a Flex class, so completing all the homework on time was a challenge at times but I was able to do it. I should have taken this class a full semester so I felt like I retained more
